asco-0.4.1

------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. INSTALLING ASCO
   ASCO is written in ANSI C. Portability on *NIX type operating systems
   should follows relatively easily. Download the latest version and at
   the command line type the following:

   tar -zxvf asco-<version>.tar.gz
   cd asco-<version>
   make


2. MANUAL
   For guidelines on how to better profit from the ASCO tool, please read
   the existing pdf manual in asco-<version>/doc/asco.pdf


3. BUGS
   Should you find a bug, please report it but first read the guidelines in
   the manual.




